      "solution": "<?php\n/**\n * Auto-generated code below aims at helping you parse\n * the standard input according to the problem statement.\n **/\nfscanf(STDIN, \"%d\", $n);\n$c = stream_get_line(STDIN, 5 + 1, \"\\n\");\n\n// construct the pattern of the bracelet\n$b = \"-\".implode('-',str_split($c));\n\n// construct the bracelet\n$bracelet = str_repeat($b,ceil($n/strlen($c))).\"-\";\n\n// cut the bracelet if too long\nif ($n%strlen($c) != 0)\n{\n    $bracelet = substr($bracelet, 0, -2*(strlen($c)-$n%strlen($c)));\n}\n\necho $bracelet;\n?>",
